media:group.media:title: From Despicable To Unforgivable  - Jake Paul's Story
media:group.media:description:
Jake Paul is one of the most hated creators on YouTube. Done strategically for more revenue, at just 19, his infamy was used to get more views and money. Though he may be wealthy, he exchanged his credibility and likability for this wealth. Now he is trying to mend his image by disowning and explaining the actions of a younger Jake Paul; his struggle to shake his prior persona.
